        </item>
        <item>
            <title>日本少女再興玩復古相機，雜訊、手震反而更有味+自創獨特新影法</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/02/retrodigitalcameras-in-japan/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=retrodigitalcameras-in-japan</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/02/retrodigitalcameras-in-japan/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 09:12:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[攝影文化]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[復古數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1284748</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在智能手機影相成為主流的今天，古典輕巧數碼相機再次「鹹魚翻生」，年輕一代並不一定靠手機攝影，有些人更會鍾情於懷舊數碼相機帶來的獨特攝影風格、效果，體驗當時的「時代感」。日本就有電視台在街頭訪問年輕用戶羣的睇法。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284766" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000018screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000018screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000018screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284767" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000023screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000023screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000023screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>現代年輕朋友反而倒造懷舊攝影產品，原因是它獨特的影像風格、時代感。在街頭訪問中，有 10 多歲、20 多歲的相機用戶分享了他們對數碼相機和智能手機的看法。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284786" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000114screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000114screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000114screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284787" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000119screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000119screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000119screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>捕捉時代感的獨特選擇</h2><p>一位受訪者提到，使用數碼相機拍攝的照片擁有特別的復古氛圍。他表示：「iPhone 拍攝時，畫面完全不會手震，但數碼相機的微微手震反而為照片增添了特殊的質感。」另一位受訪者則認為，數碼相機拍出的照片色彩和顆粒感更有故事性，「它的模糊感和類似濾鏡的效果讓畫面看起來更有趣，是一種對相片的『裝扮』」。</p><p>有受訪者表示她的相機來自她的母親：「媽媽以前買的相機現在由我使用。高中時幾乎所有同學都有一部，用它拍制服照特別有感覺。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284769" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000157screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000157screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000157screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>回憶與新潮並存</h2><p>不少路人表示，現在使用的數碼相機是從父母家中找出來的舊款型號。一位女士分享説：「我用的是媽媽以前結婚時買的數碼相機，從小就看到家裡有它，當時這些相機很普及，但隨著智能電話拍攝畫質越來越好，這些相機被冷落了。現在拿來用特別有懷舊感。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284768" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200002screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200002screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200002screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284772" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000236screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000236screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000236screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>另一位受訪者也提到：「朋友的家裡找到了舊相機，拍攝的照片有一種穿越時光的感覺，很適合分享到社交媒體。」「相比起現在的手機，數位相機拍出的照片更像懷舊電影的畫面，特別是色調和質感。」「現在我用 2006 年的數位相機拍令和時代的街景，感覺特別懷舊，甚至連快門聲都讓人想起過去的日子。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284771" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000228screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000228screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000228screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284773" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000242screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000242screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000242screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284774" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000247screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000247screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000247screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>智能手機與數碼相機的互補應用</h2><p>雖然這些復古數碼相機有其獨特魅力，受訪者也提到智能手機在一些情境下仍不可或缺。一位受訪者解釋：「室內拍照時光線不足，我通常用手機，但在光線好的地方，例如戶外，就會用復古數碼相機。」另一位受訪者分享了他的使用習慣：「我會用 iPhone 和數碼相機交替拍攝，不同設備有不同風格。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284775" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000410screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000410screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000410screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284776" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000427screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000427screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000427screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>數碼相機的時尚元素</h2><p>除了實用性，數碼相機本身的外形也成為時尚標誌。一位受訪者提到：「持有數碼相機看起來很可愛，我會在相機上掛上自製吊飾或掛件，增加個性化元素。」更有人表示，數碼相機不只是一個拍攝工具，也可用來展示個人風格。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284777" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200056screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200056screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200056screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>而數碼相機本身也成為一件復古潮流物品，很多人甚至希望將它入鏡－－在鏡子前面拍攝相片。「有些人會用鏡子反射，把復古數位相機拍進相片中，讓機身也成為作品的一部分。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284778" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000517screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000517screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000517screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284779" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000520screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000520screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000520screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284780" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000330screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000330screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000330screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>現代年輕人的復古情懷</h2><p>我們能看到數碼相機復興的背後，不只是用家們對攝影器材技術的選擇，同時是有一種回溯時代記憶的訴求。有受訪者提到，用數碼相機拍攝當下的城市風景會產生一種「時光倒流」的感覺。例如有人在使用老款相機拍攝現代的渋谷時，竟然感受到「回到平成時代」的懷舊情懷。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000247screenshot-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000247screenshot-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000247screenshot-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000317screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000317screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000317screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284782" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200038screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200038screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200038screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>復古攝影的未來</h2><p>數碼相機復古熱潮或許將會持續，尤其在更多人希望平衡現代科技與懷舊情懷時，數碼相機的獨特性成為不可替代的選擇。無論是純粹拍攝照片，還是作為展示個人品味的時尚單品，數碼相機都在新世代找到自己的位置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284784" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000524screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000524screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000524screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284785" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000110screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000110screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000110screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_90365"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DMWFp5bKdNo?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/02/retrodigitalcameras-in-japan/dc/">日本少女再興玩復古相機，雜訊、手震反而更有味+自創獨特新影法</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
